title: Pawtucket man pleads guilty to child porn
description: PAWTUCKET -- A city man has pleaded guilty to distributing and possessing child pornography, Acting U.S. Attorney for Rhode Island Sara Miron Bloom announced Wednesday.

title: Churchlands Senior High School principal warns of ‘brain drain’ risk for acclaimed music program
description: The principal of one of WA’s only selective public schools for gifted music students has warned the high quality of its 53-year-old music program is under threat from a talent ‘brain drain’.
